  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'You can find fishing spots by looking for red bouys that mark where the
    fish stock is. Once you go to a fishing spot and you see the fishing icon pop
    up, you can ''dock'' there and start a fishing minigame.

    Once you complete
    a fishing game, you need to place the item you cought in your inventory.

    There
    are 2 fishing minigames.

    The circle one speeds up the fishing progress by
    pulling (pressing F) when the needle is in the green zone.

    The hold bar
    minigame speeds up when the green box covers the moving fish. While pressing
    F, the box moves up and while not pressing, it drops down.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
